			<div class="">
				<div class="abd text-dbrown max-w-50">
					<p>Find a problem in a community, and then work with them to engineer a solution. Read more.</p>
				</div>
				<a href="#" class="block bg-dbrown rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-lblue font-semibold text-lg w-fit my-4">
					Get Started
				</a>
			</div>
			<div class=" hidden grayscale xl:block border-1 border-dbrown  
			w-full max-w-60  xl:max-w-70 2xl:max-w-90 lg:h-70 rounded-xl mt-auto  bg-[url('/images/daydream.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center group/daydream">
				<p class="w-full h-full lg:bg-linear-to-tr bg-linear-to-t from-green/20 to-yellow/30 group-hover/daydream:from-green/100 group-hover/daydream:to-yellow/70 
					rounded-xl transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out flex justify-center items-center text-center p-6 text-beige/0 group-hover/daydream:text-beige/100">
					100+ Hackers at Daydream 
				</p>

			</div>

			<div class="mt-10 grayscale border-1 border-dbrown bg-dyellow 
			grow-1 w-80 xl:max-w-180 md:max-w-full 
			h-100 lg:h-120 rounded-xl relative bg-[url('/images/jpeg.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center group/jpeg">
				<p class="w-full h-full lg:bg-linear-to-tl bg-linear-to-t from-green/20 to-yellow/30 group-hover/jpeg:from-green/100 group-hover/jpeg:to-yellow/70 
